@startuml DFD_Level2_Diet_Care_Recommendations
!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

' External Entity
actor "Pet Owner" as Owner <<External Entity>>

' Level 2 Processes for Diet & Care Recommendations (5.0)
rectangle "5.1\nAnalyze Pet\nCharacteristics" as AnalyzePet <<Process>>
rectangle "5.2\nGenerate Diet\nPlan" as GenDiet <<Process>>
rectangle "5.3\nCalculate Calorie\nNeeds" as CalcCalories <<Process>>
rectangle "5.4\nCreate Exercise\nPlan" as GenExercise <<Process>>
rectangle "5.5\nGenerate Grooming\nSchedule" as GenGrooming <<Process>>
rectangle "5.6\nCheck Allergies\n& Restrictions" as CheckAllergies <<Process>>
rectangle "5.7\nProvide Weight\nManagement" as WeightMgmt <<Process>>

' Data Stores
database "D2: Pets" as D2 <<Data Store>>
database "D4: Breed Database" as D4 <<Data Store>>
database "D11: Weight Records" as D11 <<Data Store>>
database "D12: Diet Plans" as D12 <<Data Store>>
database "D13: Allergies" as D13 <<Data Store>>

' Data Flows
Owner --> AnalyzePet : Request Recommendations\n(pet_id)

AnalyzePet --> D2 : Get Pet Data
D2 --> AnalyzePet : Breed, Age, Weight,\nActivity Level

AnalyzePet --> D4 : Query Breed Info
D4 --> AnalyzePet : Breed-Specific Needs\n(diet, exercise, grooming)

AnalyzePet --> D11 : Get Weight History
D11 --> AnalyzePet : Weight Trends, BMI

AnalyzePet --> CheckAllergies : Pet ID
CheckAllergies --> D13 : Query Allergies
D13 --> CheckAllergies : Allergen List

CheckAllergies --> GenDiet : Allergen Restrictions
AnalyzePet --> GenDiet : Pet Characteristics

GenDiet --> CalcCalories : Age, Weight, Activity Level
CalcCalories --> GenDiet : Daily Calorie Requirement
GenDiet --> D4 : Breed Diet Preferences
D4 --> GenDiet : Protein/Fat/Carb Ratios

GenDiet --> D12 : Store Diet Plan
GenDiet --> Owner : Personalized Diet Plan\n(calories, portions, food types)

AnalyzePet --> GenExercise : Breed, Age, Energy Level
GenExercise --> D4 : Breed Exercise Needs
D4 --> GenExercise : Activity Requirements
GenExercise --> Owner : Exercise Plan\n(duration, type, frequency)

AnalyzePet --> GenGrooming : Breed, Coat Type
GenGrooming --> D4 : Grooming Requirements
D4 --> GenGrooming : Brushing, Bathing Frequency
GenGrooming --> Owner : Grooming Schedule

AnalyzePet --> WeightMgmt : Current Weight, Ideal Weight
WeightMgmt --> D11 : Weight Trends
D11 --> WeightMgmt : Historical Data
WeightMgmt --> CalcCalories : Weight Goal
CalcCalories --> WeightMgmt : Adjusted Calories
WeightMgmt --> Owner : Weight Loss/Gain Plan\n(if needed)

note right of AnalyzePet
  Level 2 DFD: Diet & Care Recommendations (5.0)
  
  Sub-processes:
  5.1 - Pet characteristic analysis
  5.2 - Personalized diet plan generation
  5.3 - Calorie requirement calculation
  5.4 - Breed-specific exercise plan
  5.5 - Grooming schedule creation
  5.6 - Allergy checking and exclusions
  5.7 - Weight management recommendations
  
  Inputs Considered:
  - Breed-specific requirements
  - Age category (puppy/adult/senior)
  - Current weight vs ideal weight
  - Activity level
  - Allergies and restrictions
  - Health conditions
end note

note bottom of D4
  Breed Database includes:
  - Typical calorie needs by weight
  - Protein/fat requirements
  - Exercise needs (minutes/day)
  - Grooming frequency
  - Common food allergies
  - Health predispositions
end note

note bottom of D12
  Diet Plans table stores:
  - plan_id, pet_id, created_date
  - daily_calories, protein_grams
  - fat_grams, carbs_grams
  - meal_frequency, portion_size
  - food_type_recommendations
  - excluded_ingredients
end note

note bottom of D13
  Allergies table stores:
  - allergy_id, pet_id
  - allergen_name, severity
  - diagnosed_date, symptoms
  - alternative_ingredients
end note

@enduml
